snippet.title: Cupiclaw - Early Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2967670/Cupiclaw

Cupiclaw is a roguelike deckbuilding claw machine game. Grab, sell and add prizes in order to take on increasingly expensive new machines, until you manage to recover Morris' lost engagement ring!

Trailer music:
"Bushwick Tarantella" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
